   <div class = "entry">
      <div class="entrybody" id="https://www.accessnow.org/blog/2014/07/15/access-calls-for-president-obama-to-pledge-to-veto-cisa#When:13:30:04Z">

         <div class="entrytitle" >
            <div class="entrytitleauthor"><a href="https://www.accessnow.org/blog/rss/" title="Access Blog">Access </a></div><br />
         

