        </div>

         <div class="content">
            <p>Access and a coalition of digital rights groups, companies, and security experts submitted a letter to U.S. President Obama urging him to pledge to veto the Cybersecurity Information Sharing Act (CISA), and any other bill that includes similar provisions that would hurt our basic right to privacy.</p>
          </div>
                        
         <p align="right">
            <a href="https://www.accessnow.org/blog/2014/07/15/access-calls-for-president-obama-to-pledge-to-veto-cisa">
