         <div class="entrytitle" >
            <div class="entrytitleauthor"><a href="https://guardianproject.info/" title="The Guardian Project">Guardian Project </a></div><br />
                     <img class="face" src="http://openitp.org/img/guardian_circle.png" width="" height="" alt="">

            <a href="https://guardianproject.info/2014/06/04/reset-the-net/">Reset The Net!</a> 
        </div>

         <div class="content">
            <p>We&#8217;re making the Internet more secure, by taking part in #ResetTheNet <a href="https://resetthenet.org">https://resetthenet.org</a> </p>
<p/>
          </div>
                        
         <p align="right">
            <a href="https://guardianproject.info/2014/06/04/reset-the-net/">
